cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.SY, cs.LG, cs.AI. 

The paper discusses Simultaneous Localization and Mapping (SLAM), which is a problem in robotics and computer vision. Therefore, cs.RO (Robotics) and cs.CV (Computer Vision) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also discusses control systems and approximation techniques, which fall under cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) respectively. Finally, the paper uses domain knowledge to improve approximation, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
